<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="394">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lin-xiu-shu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lin-xiu-shu" class="zg-link" title="林秀树">林秀树</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$sun-da-ran-90" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/sun-da-ran-90" class="zg-link" title="孙大然">孙大然</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


